{"tid":1878921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那肺炎個案增至逾6萬4千宗　湖北延遲復工復課","createTime":"2020-02-14T01:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T01:57:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e04a65698181414d03aa9bc1ec6ebc0503df07","tid":1878921,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"支那肺炎疫情持續，當地公布近6萬4千人確診，比昨日多近5千人，死亡個案增至近1500宗。在重災區湖北省，昨日新增4800多宗確診個案，累計近52000宗。省疫情防控指揮部發布通告，延遲企業復工和學校開學，要求省內各類企業不可早於下星期四前復工。<br />\n<br />\n通告表示，除了涉及疫情防控必需的醫療、藥品，以及超市等企業之外，其餘企業都需要按規定延遲復工復課，以有效減少人員流動聚集，阻斷疫情傳播。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在北京，當局要求三類場所，即時起落實25項防疫工作，包括商務樓宇、商場和餐館，並且由本月10日起開展監督。"},{"pid":"de0cfdf3bdb85abd036e722f7ca171eb08003234","tid":1878921,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:17:38.000Z","msg":"比前一日增加15000宗數目大減 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ip6V1na.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fip6V1na.jpg&h=a90f2fa3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1841284e5cda57a9202cdef9c541f517fa091bbf","tid":1878921,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:19:03.000Z","msg":"唔撚係呀<br />\n大陸啲廠唔開，我地食風呀"},{"pid":"dddecc1ec4c5bc27df7cb9718d40eb1e658f7cce","tid":1878921,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:19:09.000Z","msg":"湖北睇黎真係由佢自生自滅"},{"pid":"b9a01d6e22b598b3bb0adff377570e9635c47543","tid":1878921,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de0cfdf3bdb85abd036e722f7ca171eb08003234","tid":1878921,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:17:38.000Z","msg":"比前一日增加15000宗數目大減 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ip6V1na.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fip6V1na.jpg&h=a90f2fa3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:21:03.000Z","msg":"國家要復工，全國除湖北省外，焗住個數字要降。但湖北郁左個話事人，又延後復工復課，自然可以放比較真實少少既數據，因人已死，有得懶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b511cfc3a07cacd902ab1620b7dddd86df439f","tid":1878921,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dddecc1ec4c5bc27df7cb9718d40eb1e658f7cce","tid":1878921,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:19:09.000Z","msg":"湖北睇黎真係由佢自生自滅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:22:52.000Z","msg":"冇有效治療方法 咪等佢乜藥都試<br />\n醫唔醫到都係賭大細咁"},{"pid":"dcc15e147ea6b742bfa75c7701b176a88e8184f5","tid":1878921,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:24:14.000Z","msg":"支共識玩 一日增長15000個案, 跟住所有日子都係下降"},{"pid":"28f31417d90e5b18ab533269fed29936ebc4a9d7","tid":1878921,"uid":164266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"應勇上任之後應該將之前瞞報果d爆曬出來，唔係的話咁多單做檢測都做唔切啦"},{"pid":"5d2437b40f9d4b2fbb2e0c05fab4825affb73685","tid":1878921,"uid":325192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28f31417d90e5b18ab533269fed29936ebc4a9d7","tid":1878921,"uid":164266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"應勇上任之後應該將之前瞞報果d爆曬出來，唔係的話咁多單做檢測都做唔切啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:44:53.000Z","msg":"正確做法，冇可能幫上手食屎"},{"pid":"732e0a8d7b52efb4cbfcaa41b0d60c1ddb1e0404","tid":1878921,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:46:25.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多測試劑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6da018deb4f5994a1597ae4bebbe22ea38a9b7","tid":1878921,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:47:30.000Z","msg":"湖北省 已經被放棄治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n湖北人 你們可以死了"},{"pid":"2387e564890ef15a465d5554f6a37d412808765c","tid":1878921,"uid":39365,"like":0,"d